item.description:
@Daginith wrote:

[quote=“dylan_0789, post:4, topic:435331”][quote author=Daginith link=topic=538051.msg3936237#msg3936237 date=1331070313]

You could:

a) Search harder
b) Decompile and rip them from somebody else’s client
c) Make your own

Literally. I’ve seen these on at least ten servers.

I don’t suggest C. He’ll end up making ones with crappy wire frames and 100B faces. ;D
[/quote]
So you are suggesting he leeches someone elses models as opposed to learning how to model? You should be encouraging him to learn how to model.[/quote]

Its not leeching if you give credits ;D
